\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fpen\u002FPopawrR'>Vue3 Composition API\u003C\u002Fa> by Ray\n  (\u003Ca href='https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\u002Fhsiangfeng'>@hsiangfeng\u003C\u002Fa>) on \u003Ca href='https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io'>CodePen\u003C\u002Fa>.\n",[16,411,412],{},"那我們這邊只是稍微提到兩種版本的寫法差異，所以大概知道一下就可以了。",[12,414,416],{"id":415},"vue2-defineproperty","Vue2 defineProperty",[16,418,419],{},"接下來聊聊 Vue2 v-model 是如何實作的，Vue2 的 v-model 實作最主要關鍵技術在於以下：",[421,422,423,429],"ul",{},[424,425,426],"li",{},[20,427,428],{},"Object.defineProperty",[424,430,431,434,435],{},[20,432,433],{},"Getter"," 與 ",[20,436,437],{},"Setter",[16,439,440,441,445],{},"但是這邊就不太過深入說明，因為在先前的文章已經有詳細說過了，所以如果對於這兩個不熟悉的話，建議可以閱讀我先前寫的 ",[35,442,444],{"href":443},"\u002Ftags\u002F%E7%89%A9%E4%BB%B6%E5%B1%AC%E6%80%A7%E5%BB%B6%E4%BC%B8%E7%AB%A0%E7%AF%80%EF%BC%9A%E5%B1%AC%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%B5\u002F","文章"," 都有介紹到。",[16,447,448],{},"那麼這一段該如何自己實作呢？讓我們來試著製作看看，首先來看看我們 HTMl 結構，當然要模仿當然要模仿得像一點：",[74,450,452],{"className":76,"code":451,"language":78,"meta":79,"style":79},"\u003Cdiv id=\"app\">\n  我的名字是：\u003Cspan v-model=\"myName\">\u003C\u002Fspan>\n  \u003Cbr>\n  \u003Cinput type=\"text\" v-model=\"myName\">\n\u003C\u002Fdiv>\n",[20,453,454,468,488,496,516],{"__ignoreMap":79},[83,455,456,458,460,462,464,466],{"class":85,"line":86},[83,457,90],{"class":89},[83,459,94],{"class":93},[83,461,98],{"class":97},[83,463,101],{"class":89},[83,465,105],{"class":104},[83,467,108],{"class":89},[83,469,470,473,475,477,479,481,484,486],{"class":85,"line":111},[83,471,472],{"class":89},"  我的名字是：\u003C",[83,474,83],{"class":93},[83,476,144],{"class":97},[83,478,101],{"class":89},[83,480,149],{"class":104},[83,482,483],{"class":89},">\u003C\u002F",[83,485,83],{"class":93},[83,487,108],{"class":89},[83,489,490,492,494],{"class":85,"line":117},[83,491,120],{"class":89},[83,493,123],{"class":93},[83,495,108],{"class":89},[83,497,498,500,502,504,506,508,510,512,514],{"class":85,"line":128},[83,499,120],{"class":89},[83,501,133],{"clas